	<!-- Counselling -->
    <div class="row pt-4 pb-4" id="counselling" style="background:#ced4f8; overflow-x:hidden;">
        <div class="col margined-page image-text-section" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
            <img class="" src="~/img/our-services/counselling.jpg" style=" width:100%;" />

        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 image-text-section" style="overflow-y:auto;">

            <h3 class="pt-5">Counselling</h3>
            <p>
                Our team of experienced counselors provides a safe and supportive environment for individuals, couples, and families. Our counseling services include the following.
            </p>

            <strong> Individual Counseling </strong>
            <p>
                Tailored support for personal challenges and growth.
            </p>
            <strong>Couples Counseling </strong>
            <p>Strengthen your relationship and communication with your partner. </p>
            <strong>Family Therapy </strong>
            <p>Resolve conflicts and improve family dynamics. </p>
            <strong>Trauma & Grief Counseling</strong>
            <p>Compassionate assistance for coping with trauma and loss. </p>
