            <p> Learn techniques to manage anxiety and stress effectively. </p>
            <strong>Depression & Mood Disorder</strong>
            <p> Support and strategies for those facing mood-related challenges. </p>
            <strong>LGBTQ+ Support </strong>
            <p>Inclusive and affirming counseling for the LGBTQ+ community.</p>

        </div>
	</div>
	<!-- Family planning -->
    <div class="row white-bg row pt-4 pb-4" id="family-planning">
        <div class="col margined-page image-text-section">

            <h3 class="pt-5">Family Planning Services</h3>
            <p> At E-nompilo Healthcare Centre, we understand the importance of family planning and offer a variety of options to help you make the right choice for your family's future. Our family planning services include the following. </p>

            <strong>IUD (Merena) 5 Years</strong>
            <p>A long-acting and reversible contraception method that offers up to 5 years of protection. </p>

            <strong>IUD (Copper) 10 Years</strong>

            <p>A highly effective and long-lasting contraceptive option that provides up to 10 years of protection. </p>

            <strong>Implant 3 Years</strong>

            <p>A discreet and reliable contraceptive implant that lasts for up to 3 years.</p>

            <strong>Injection 3 Months</strong>

            <p>Convenient and effective birth control through regular injections. </p>

            <strong>Ring 3 Weeks</strong>

            <p>A hormonal birth control ring that you replace every 3 weeks. </p>

            <strong>Patch 1 Week</strong>

            <p>A contraceptive patch that you change weekly.</p>

            <strong>Oral Contraceptive 28 Days</strong>

            <p>Traditional birth control pills taken daily for 28 days. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col margined-page image-text-section" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
